jpaechnatz","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/jpaechnatz/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/jpaechnatz/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/jpaechnatz/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/jpaechnatz/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/jpaechnatz/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/jpaechnatz/orgs","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/jpaechnatz/repos","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/jpaechnatz/events{/privacy}","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/jpaechnatz/received_events","type":"user","site_admin":false},"created_at":"2013-06-11t08:47:29z","updated_at":"2013-06-11t08:47:29z","body":"these are the specs and not a documentation, which is needed before enableing the encryption.\r\n\r\nas stated in the specs, there maybe problems in the case of owncloud updates/upgrades and the update hooks.\r\n\r\nor as example, the syncclient... not answered... when looking at it, i could guess it uses a kind of webdav....  and so \"part files are not compatible with files_encrytion's key management system however, so \r\n  we have to always sanitise such paths manually before using them.\" what does that mean to users and me.\r\n\r\ni really like to test encryption on my site, currently with 10 users, family members and work colleagues...but with that few information you couldn't expect that some one risk a blind flight, not knowing if the whole site/data is wrecked afterwards.\r\n\r\nremember good press, the german middle-sized companies are now in a good mood to try local cloud services on their own hardware... only encryption is missed. ;-)\r\n"},{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/owncloud/core/issues/comments/19249450","html_url":"https://github.com/owncloud/core/issues/3626#issuecomment-19249450","issue_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/owncloud/core/issues/3626","id":19249450,"user":{"login":"georgehrke","id":1250540,"avatar_url":"https://gravatar.com/avatar/6cfab50556db1530130dfd5d0398b069?d=https%3a%2f%2fidenticons.github.com%2fd32c0eeb36fb0c7401756c23e51e50fb.png&r=x","gravatar_id":"6cfab50556db1530130dfd5d0398b069","url":"https://api.github.com/users/georgehrke","html_url":"https://github.com/georgehrke","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/georgehrke/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/georgehrke/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/georgehrke/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/georgehrke/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/georgehrke/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/georgehrke/orgs","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/georgehrke/repos","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/georgehrke/events{/privacy}","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/georgehrke/received_events","type":"user","site_admin":false},"created_at":"2013-06-11t08:49:40z","updated_at":"2013-06-11t08:49:40z","body":"i guess @schiesbn will be able to answer your questions."},{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/owncloud/core/issues/comments/19249642","html_url":"https://github.com/owncloud/core/issues/3626#issuecomment-19249642","issue_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/owncloud/core/issues/3626","id":19249642,"user":{"login":"realrancor","id":2248459,"avatar_url":"https://gravatar.com/avatar/f6105e79dfcfb0fcbabb3db061135c08?d=https%3a%2f%2fidenticons.github.com%2f7a70061016eba74d85c060de0f65212d.png&r=x","gravatar_id":"f6105e79dfcfb0fcbabb3db061135c08","url":"https://api.github.com/users/realrancor","html_url":"https://github.com/realrancor","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/realrancor/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/realrancor/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/realrancor/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/realrancor/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/realrancor/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/realrancor/orgs","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/realrancor/repos","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/realrancor/events{/privacy}","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/realrancor/received_events","type":"user","site_admin":false},"created_at":"2013-06-11t08:54:22z","updated_at":"2013-06-11t09:24:19z","body":"an introduction by schiesbn can be found here:\r\n\r\nhttp://blog.schiessle.org/2013/05/28/introduction-to-the-new-owncloud-encryption-app/\r\n\r\nthe important part is:\r\n\r\n>  this means that the encrypt and decrypt happens transparently so that you can still use all the other features from owncloud like sharing, different viewer apps, webdav access etc.\r\n\r\nwhich should answer most of your questions. only this not not answered:\r\n\r\n> is it enabled for all users and all files/folders?\r\n> or is it limited to specific folders?\r\n\r\nafaik if you enable the encryption app all files of all users are encrypted."},{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/owncloud/core/issues/comments/19252916","html_url":"https://github.com/owncloud/core/issues/3626#issuecomment-19252916","issue_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/owncloud/core/issues/3626","id":19252916,"user":{"login":"schiesbn","id":1589737,"avatar_url":"https://gravatar.com/avatar/8912b598c7b32dd25b87fd168e0b06b2?d=https%3a%2f%2fidenticons.github.com%2f0a323047dbe8329db30eae8dbe96e55e.png&r=x","gravatar_id":"8912b598c7b32dd25b87fd168e0b06b2","url":"https://api.github.com/users/schiesbn","html_url":"https://github.com/schiesbn","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/schiesbn/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/schiesbn/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/schiesbn/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/schiesbn/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/schiesbn/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/schiesbn/orgs","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/schiesbn/repos","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/schiesbn/events{/privacy}","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/schiesbn/received_events","type":"user","site_admin":false},"created_at":"2013-06-11t10:15:23z","updated_at":"2013-06-11t10:15:23z","body":"@jpaechnatz i would recommend the blog mentioned by @realrancor  ;-)\r\n\r\nif the encryption is enabled all files and folders will be encrypted once the user log-in for the first time. so the first log-in after enabling the encryption app can take some time, be patience.\r\n\r\nsharing, sync client, etc. also works with the encryption app.\r\n\r\nsome information which you will not find in the blog:\r\n\r\nif you are using the sync client i would recommend to shut down the client before enabling the encryption app and before your first log-in. otherwise it could happen that your files get encrypted multiple times. after the initial encryption you can start the sync client again. a fix is already on the way."},{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/owncloud/core/issues/comments/19379594","html_url":"https://github.com/owncloud/core/issues/3626#issuecomment-19379594","issue_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/owncloud/core/issues/3626","id":19379594,"user":{"login":"jpaechnatz","id":2646767,"avatar_url":"https://gravatar.com/avatar/aac43c081c5d914d989e1b2727e74008?d=https%3a%2f%2fidenticons.github.com%2f112ef05882d35a8a556a75c30fcea042.png&r=x","gravatar_id":"aac43c081c5d914d989e1b2727e74008","url":"https://api.github.com/users/jpaechnatz","html_url":"https://github.com/jpaechnatz","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/jpaechnatz/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/jpaechnatz/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/jpaechnatz/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/jpaechnatz/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/jpaechnatz/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/jpaechnatz/orgs","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/jpaechnatz/repos","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/jpaechnatz/events{/privacy}","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/jpaechnatz/received_events","type":"user","site_admin":false},"created_at":"2013-06-13t08:53:11z","updated_at":"2013-06-13t08:53:11z","body":"and perhaps a last question... ;-)\r\n\r\nupdating owncloud from 5.0.7 to 5.0.x ... the specs mentions not working update/upgrade hooks... so what does that mean in the case of an upgrade?\r\n\r\n- new version installed\r\n- all apps disabled, migration runs, all files decrypted.\r\n- login all former apps enabled, all files getting encrypted again?\r\n\r\n"},{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/owncloud/core/issues/comments/19381349","html_url":"https://github.com/owncloud/core/issues/3626#issuecomment-19381349","issue_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/owncloud/core/issues/3626","id":19381349,"user":{"login":"schiesbn","id":1589737,"avatar_url":"https://gravatar.com/avatar/8912b598c7b32dd25b87fd168e0b06b2?d=https%3a%2f%2fidenticons.github.com%2f0a323047dbe8329db30eae8dbe96e55e.png&r=x","gravatar_id":"8912b598c7b32dd25b87fd168e0b06b2","url":"https://api.github.com/users/schiesbn","html_url":"https://github.com/schiesbn","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/schiesbn/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/schiesbn/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/schiesbn/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/schiesbn/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/schiesbn/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/schiesbn/orgs","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/schiesbn/repos","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/schiesbn/events{/privacy}","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/schiesbn/received_events","type":"user","site_admin":false},"created_at":"2013-06-13t09:32:12z","updated_at":"2013-06-13t09:32:47z","body":"> login all former apps enabled, all files getting encrypted again?\r\n\r\nno, during initial encryption owncloud can distinguish between already encrypted files, files encrypted with the old encryption and plain files and act accordingly. further the migration status is stored in the database. this should not be changed during upgrade so the initial encryption should not start at all in this case."},{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/owncloud/core/issues/comments/24891334","html_url":"https://github.com/owncloud/core/issues/3626#issuecomment-24891334","issue_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/owncloud/core/issues/3626","id":24891334,"user":{"login":"kabum","id":245432,"avatar_url":"https://gravatar.com/avatar/a1dea19f88f38ea0b5b5b4d19d5b3107?d=https%3a%2f%2fidenticons.github.com%2f53d8cbb3dbc087a02951dec47438ccdf.png&r=x","gravatar_id":"a1dea19f88f38ea0b5b5b4d19d5b3107","url":"https://api.github.com/users/kabum","html_url":"https://github.com/kabum","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/kabum/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/kabum/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/kabum/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/kabum/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/kabum/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/kabum/orgs","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/kabum/repos","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/kabum/events{/privacy}","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/kabum/received_events","type":"user","site_admin":false},"created_at":"2013-09-22t21:43:52z","updated_at":"2013-09-22t21:43:52z","body":"please reopen if the problem isn't solved."}]